{"tid":2421200,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"曾被校方威脅有權 DQ　中大學生會內閣「朔夜」當選　候任會長林睿晞：校方沒法抹煞選票力量","createTime":"2021-02-24T10:55:03.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-24T14:02:42.000Z","uid":51271,"like":25,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"56b55e2510c0eb61a382b42ae83a185aba1ea092","tid":2421200,"uid":51271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-24T10:55:03.000Z","msg":"中大學生會投票期今日（24 日）結束，早前曾遭校方警告其言論或違法，有權終止員生或組織職務的內閣「朔夜」，以 3,983 信任票當選。<br />\n<br />\n候任會長林睿晞表示，得票數是自 2014 年以來最高，顯示中大選民肯定他們的路線及理念，同學在校方威脅之下仍勇敢投票，「民意係應該用嚟尊重，而唔係俾你踐踏，我相信呢個係校方必須要清楚知道嘅現實」。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/politics/曾被校方威脅有權-dq-中大學生會內閣-朔夜-當選-候任會長林睿晞-校方沒法抹煞選票力量/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%E6%9B%BE%E8%A2%AB%E6%A0%A1%E6%96%B9%E5%A8%81%E8%84%85%E6%9C%89%E6%AC%8A-dq-%E4%B8%AD%E5%A4%A7%E5%AD%B8%E7%94%9F%E6%9C%83%E5%85%A7%E9%96%A3-%E6%9C%94%E5%A4%9C-%E7%95%B6%E9%81%B8-%E5%80%99%E4%BB%BB%E6%9C%83%E9%95%B7%E6%9E%97%E7%9D%BF%E6%99%9E-%E6%A0%A1%E6%96%B9%E6%B2%92%E6%B3%95%E6%8A%B9%E7%85%9E%E9%81%B8%E7%A5%A8%E5%8A%9B%E9%87%8F%2F&d=s5X1yiNR%2BigbIA3iGijs8MwxwlTbS8X6vvpFIqFCSYY%3D&h=e5b13819\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%E6%9B%BE%E8%A2%AB%E6%A0%A1%E6%96%B9%E5%A8%81%E8%84%85%E6%9C%89%E6%AC%8A-dq-%E4%B8%AD%E5%A4%A7%E5%AD%B8%E7%94%9F%E6%9C%83%E5%85%A7%E9%96%A3-%E6%9C%94%E5%A4%9C-%E7%95%B6%E9%81%B8-%E5%80%99%E4%BB%BB%E6%9C%83%E9%95%B7%E6%9E%97%E7%9D%BF%E6%99%9E-%E6%A0%A1%E6%96%B9%E6%B2%92%E6%B3%95%E6%8A%B9%E7%85%9E%E9%81%B8%E7%A5%A8%E5%8A%9B%E9%87%8F%2F&h=9646d644\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.thestandnews.com/politics/曾被校方威脅有權-dq-中大學生會內閣-朔夜-當選-候任會長林睿晞-校方沒法抹煞選票力量/</a>"},{"pid":"82e61aec7aff6d63e6539afeee5bdd462bd26ebc","tid":2421200,"uid":54876,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-24T10:55:46.000Z","msg":"3900咁多"},{"pid":"3fbd04c2f3a779bd3bbdf24cb803dfddadf6a6bf","tid":2421200,"uid":292292,"like":0